snippet.title: Super Cucumber Gameplay Trailer (June 2023)
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for Super Cucumber, a 16-bit inspired action platformer currently set to release for Windows and the Steam Deck in 2024.

You can Wishlist Super Cucumber Now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/522290/Super_Cucumber/
